<section xml:id="activity-function-notation" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
    <title>Function Notation (Input, Output)</title>

    <subsection xml:id="subsection-what-is-a-function">
        <title>What is a Function?</title>

        <p>A function is a rule, like a formula or a graph or a table of values, that assigns an ouput value for a given input.</p>
        <p>The formula <m>y = 2^{x}</m> is a function because if you pick an input like <m>x=3</m>, you get an ouput <m>y=8</m>. (since <m>8= 2^{3}</m>) </p>

    </subsection>
</section>
